    <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
    <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> October 16, 2024</p>

    <h2>1. Service Description</h2>
    <p>krtk.rs is a URL shortening service provided as a demonstration application. This service comes with no warranty and is provided "as is".</p>

    <h2>2. Data Collection</h2>
    <p>We collect:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Original URLs that you submit for shortening</li>
        <li>Timestamps of when URLs are created</li>
        <li>Basic usage analytics</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Data is retained indefinitely unless manually deleted by the service operator.</p>

    <h2>3. Data Sharing</h2>
    <p>We do not share your data with any third parties.</p>

    <h2>4. Prohibited Uses</h2>
    <p>You may not use this service to shorten URLs that:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Contain malware, viruses, or other harmful software</li>
        <li>Are used for phishing or fraudulent activities</li>
        <li>Violate any applicable laws or regulations</li>
        <li>Infringe on intellectual property rights</li>
        <li>Contain spam or unsolicited commercial content</li>
        <li>Are used to harass, abuse, or harm others</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>5. Service Availability</h2>
    <p>This is a demonstration service with no uptime guarantees. The service may be discontinued at any time without notice.</p>

    <h2>6. Limitation of Liability</h2>
    <p>This service is provided without warranty of any kind. We are not liable for any damages arising from the use of this service.</p>

    <h2>7. Termination</h2>
    <p>We reserve the right to remove any shortened URLs and terminate access for violations of these terms.</p>

